    "updated_at": "2015-03-17T04:11:32Z",
    "body": "It is possible to achieve it with _considerable_ work, but the menu API in atom-shell meant to show **native** menus, if you want custom menus, you should implement it with HTML and CSS, just like what Brackets did.\n\nSo I'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
