    "created_at": "2015-12-19T01:39:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-19T01:39:00Z",
    "body": "> Being able to change the color of a menu is important in Windows. Very few applications on Windows leave the default menu bar color as the default\n\nYep! And they're all owner-drawn, custom menus. Implementing our own one-off, custom menus with the sole capability of changing a background color as their distinguishing feature seems ill-advised\n"
