    "created_at": "2015-12-19T02:24:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-19T02:24:18Z",
    "body": "If you just don't want to cater to Windows - I get that, but it seems like you're already catering to OS X where necessary with things like a special object model for their wonky (IMO) global menu system.\n\nMenus are just attached to their windows in Windows, so allowing just the most basic customizations on them would go a long way.\n"
